lude concertos by the following composers:\n\n==Baroque==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n*[[Tomaso Albinoni]]\n*[[Johann Sebastian Bach]]\n*[[Arcangelo Corelli]] (arranged by [[John Barbirolli]] from Corelli's [[Twelve Violin Sonatas, Op.5 (Corelli)|Violin Sonatas, Op. 5]])\n*[[Joseph-Hector Fiocco]]\n*[[Christoph Graupner]]\n*[[George Frideric Handel]]\n*[[Antonio Lotti]]\n*[[Alessandro Marcello]]\n*[[Johann Joachim Quantz]]\n*[[Alessandro Scarlatti]]\n*[[Georg Philipp Telemann]]\n*[[Antonio Vivaldi]]\n*[[Jan Dismas Zelenka]]\n{{col-2}}\n{{listen\n | filename     = Albinoni_-_Concerto for 2 Oboes in F Major, op. 9 No. 3 - 1. Allegro.ogg\n | title        = Concerto for 2 Oboes in F Major, Op.&nbsp;9, No. 3 - 1. Allegro\n | description  = [[Tomaso Albinoni]]'s Concerto for Two Oboes in F major. Performed by the Advent Chamber Orchestra with oboists Humbert Lucarelli and Edino Biaggi\n | filename2    = Albinoni_-_Concerto for 2 Oboes in F Major, op. 9 No. 3 - 2. Adagio.ogg\n | title2       = Concerto for 2 Oboes in F Major, Op.&nbsp;9, No. 3 - 2. Adagio\n | description2 = \n | filename3    = Albinoni_-_Concerto for 2 Oboes in F Major, op. 9 No. 3 - 3. Allegro.ogg\n | title3       = Concerto for 2 Oboes in F Major, Op.&nbsp;9, No. 3 - 3. Allegro\n | description3 =\n|filename4    = Vivaldi - Concerto for Oboe and Orchestra in C major F7-6 - 2. Andante.ogg\n|title4       = Vivaldi's Concerto for Oboe and Orchestra in C major (RV 447) - 2. Andante\n|description4 = The 2nd movement of [[Antonio Vivaldi]]'s Oboe Concerto in C major, RV 447, Performed by the Advent Chamber Orchestra with oboist Edino Biaggi\n}}\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Classical==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n*[[Carl Philipp Emanuel Bach]]\n*[[Johann Christian Bach]]\n*[[Ludwig van Beethoven]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.usatoday.com/news/world/2003-03-02-beethoven_x.htm|title=Beethoven's lost oboe concerto performed|publisher=USA Today|date=March 2, 2003|accessdate=2015-11-14}}</ref>\n*[[Carlo Besozzi]]\n*[[Domenico Cimarosa]]\n*[[Carl Ditters von Dittersdorf]]\n*[[Josef Fiala]]\n*[[Joseph Haydn]] ([[Oboe Concerto (Haydn)|spurious]])\n*[[William Herschel]]\n*[[Franz Anton Hoffmeister]]\n{{col-2}}\n*[[Ignaz Holzbauer]]\n*[[Johann Nepomuk Hummel]]\n*[[Jan Anton\u00edn Ko\u017eeluh]]\n*[[Franz Krommer]]\n*[[Ludwig August Lebrun]]\n*[[Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart]]\n*[[Antonio Rosetti]]\n*[[Antonio Salieri]]\n*[[Carl Stamitz]]\n*[[Peter von Winter]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Romantic==\n{{Listen|filename=Antonio Pasculli - Gran Concerto.ogg|title=Antonio Pasculli - Gran Concerto|description=[[Antonio Pasculli]]'s Gran Concerto. Performed by [[Alex Klein]], oboe, and Lisa Bergman, piano}}\n\n*[[Vincenzo Bellini]]\n*[[Jan Kalivoda]]\n*[[August Klughardt]]\n*[[Bernhard Molique]]\n*[[Ignaz Moscheles]]\n*[[Antonio Pasculli]]\n*[[Nikolai Rimsky-Korsakov]] (oboe and band)\n*[[Richard Strauss]]\n*[[Stanislas Verroust]]\n*[[Carl Maria von Weber]] (with winds)\n\n==Contemporary==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-3}}\n*[[Kalevi Aho]]\n*[[William Alwyn]]\n*[[David Amram]]\n*[[Hendrik Andriessen]]\n*[[Louis Andriessen]]\n*[[Malcolm Arnold]]\n*[[Tadeusz Baird]]\n*[[Leonardo Balada]]\n*[[Samuel Barber]]\n*[[Sally Beamish]]\n*[[David Bedford]]\n*[[Arthur Benjamin]] (on themes of [[Domenico Cimarosa]])\n*[[Richard Rodney Bennett]]\n*[[Luciano Berio]]\n*[[Lennox Berkeley]]\n*[[Michael Berkeley]]\n*[[John Biggs (composer)|John Biggs]]\n*[[Judith Bingham]]\n*[[Anthony Burgess]]\n*[[Edwin Carr (composer)|Edwin Carr]]\n*[[Elliott Carter]]<ref>{{Cite web |last=Carter |first=Elliott |authorlink=Elliott Carter |year=1987 |title=Oboe Concerto: Programme Note |publisher=[[Boosey & Hawkes]] |url=http://www.boosey.com/cr/music/Elliott-Carter-Oboe-Concerto/6516 |accessdate=November 5, 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Mario Castelnuovo-Tedesco]]\n*[[John Corigliano]]<ref>{{cite book |last=Corigliano |first=John |authorlink=John Corigliano |title=Concerto for Oboe and Orchestra (1975) |url=http://www.musicsalesclassical.com/composer/work/26970 |publis